commitResults.messageTitle: Add List and Mark as Done feature
commitResults.messageBody:
Implement the ability to list tasks and mark them as done.

The List feature allows users to view all tasks they have added.

The Mark as Done feature enables users to mark individual tasks as
completed.

These features enhance the overall functionality of the Chatbot.

Need ways for user to categorize their tasks.

Users can categorize their tasks into 3 types.

Allow users to track their daily tasks comprehensively.

Simplify debugging process.

Automated test cases help to evaluate code correctness quickly.

Assist developer by reducing debugging effort and time.
